WEBVTT

00:34.469 --> 00:36.427
DINGER.

00:36.471 --> 00:39.126
DINGER, WAKE UP FOR A MINUTE.
I GOTTA TALK TO YOU, BUDDY.

00:39.169 --> 00:41.432
LOOK, BOBBY,
I'M ASLEEP.

00:41.476 --> 00:43.695
I'M SOUND ASLEEP,
BOBBY.

00:43.739 --> 00:45.697
I'M DREAMING.

00:45.741 --> 00:50.311
APACHE WOMEN,
MAI TAIS,

00:50.354 --> 00:53.053
VANNA WHITE
AND A WHIP.

00:58.101 --> 01:01.017
I'M IN LOVE.

01:01.061 --> 01:03.454
THAT COULD BE A PROBLEM.

01:03.498 --> 01:05.630
I DON'T THINK
YOU UNDERSTAND.

01:05.674 --> 01:07.980
NO, NO, I DO UNDERSTAND.
I REALLY DO.

01:08.024 --> 01:10.461
WHICH HAND IS IT
THIS WEEK, POWELL?

01:16.250 --> 01:18.208
YOU'RE IN LOVE
WITH LAINIE?

01:18.252 --> 01:19.775
LAINIE?
LAINIE DIAMOND?

01:19.818 --> 01:21.690
I CAN'T BELIEVE WHAT
I'M HEARING HERE, BOBBY.

01:21.733 --> 01:23.561
ARE WE TALKING ABOUT JOEL'S LAINIE?

01:23.605 --> 01:25.694
HOLD ON, ARE WE TALKING
ABOUT LAINIE...

01:25.737 --> 01:27.913
THE ONE THAT LOOKS GREAT
IN A LEOTARD LAINIE?

01:27.957 --> 01:30.829
YEAH, GREAT, SHE LOOKS
FABULOUS IN A LEOTARD.

01:30.873 --> 01:33.180
SHE'S JOEL'S.
YOU HAVE ANY IDEA WHO JOEL IS...

01:33.223 --> 01:35.486
JOEL, JOEL,
PSYCHO JOEL?

01:35.530 --> 01:37.532
JOEL'S GONNA KILL ME.

01:37.575 --> 01:39.577
JOEL'S GONNA
WALK IN HERE

01:39.621 --> 01:41.623
AND KILL BOTH OF US
AT THE SAME TIME.

01:47.324 --> 01:50.545
HE DIDN'T MEAN ANYTHING ABOUT LAINIE.
JUST RELAX. JUST RELAX.

01:50.588 --> 01:53.113
ARE YOU DONE WITH YOUR
INDIAN MATING RITUAL YET?

01:53.156 --> 01:55.724
YOU KNOW, WHY DOES EVERYTHING
YOU HAVE TO SAY...

01:55.767 --> 01:58.161
WHY DOES IT HAVE TO
REVOLVE AROUND SEX?

01:58.205 --> 02:00.816
WHY? WHY ARE YOU
SO PERVERTED?

02:07.170 --> 02:09.607
IT HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH SEX.

02:09.651 --> 02:11.261
IT HAS TO DO
WITH THE FACT

02:11.305 --> 02:13.220
THAT I AM TOTALLY
IN LOVE WITH...

02:13.263 --> 02:16.005
NO, NO.
LOOK, DON'T SAY HER NAME, ALL RIGHT?

02:16.048 --> 02:18.399
DON'T THINK ABOUT HER.
DON'T TALK ABOUT HER.

02:18.442 --> 02:20.488
GET HER OUT OF
YOUR HEAD.

02:20.531 --> 02:21.706
- OKAY.
- OKAY?

02:21.750 --> 02:22.881
- OKAY.
- YOU PROMISE?

02:22.925 --> 02:24.056
- PROMISE.
- OKAY.

02:24.100 --> 02:26.102
OKAY.

02:27.756 --> 02:29.888
- LAINIE, LAINIE, LAINIE.
- NO, NO.

02:29.932 --> 02:31.107
- NO!
- HEH!

02:38.114 --> 02:41.857
WHAT WAS THAT
"HEH" SOUND, BOBBY?

02:41.900 --> 02:43.859
HEH!
THAT'S THE WAY I LAUGH.

02:43.902 --> 02:45.861
YOU KNOW... HEH!

02:45.904 --> 02:48.690
WHAT THE HELL IS "HEH"?
WHY CAN'T YOU LAUGH LIKE A MAN?

02:56.001 --> 02:57.351
- Bobby: READY?
- Dinger: NO.

02:57.394 --> 02:59.135
- LET'S GO.
- ALL RIGHT.

02:59.179 --> 03:01.224
Bobby:
ONE, TWO, TOO-DOO-DOO.

03:01.268 --> 03:03.226
[ imitates guitar riff ]

03:03.270 --> 03:06.360
♪ OH, OUR LIFE IS TOUGH ♪

03:06.403 --> 03:08.449
[ imitates guitar riff ]

03:08.492 --> 03:10.668
♪ MONEY NEVER SEEMS TO BE ENOUGH ♪

03:10.712 --> 03:12.670
[ imitates guitar riff ]

03:12.714 --> 03:15.325
♪ AND IF I COULD HAVE,
OH, JUST ONE THING ♪

03:15.369 --> 03:17.327
[ imitates guitar riff ]

03:17.371 --> 03:20.156
♪ HOLY GOD, I WISH
YOU COULD SING ♪

03:24.987 --> 03:27.555
NO, NO, KEEP GOING.
GIVE ME MORE THAN THAT.

03:27.598 --> 03:29.774
I'M FLUNKING EVERY GRADE
IN SCHOOL.

03:29.818 --> 03:31.559
MARVELOUS.
SO AM I.

03:31.602 --> 03:33.517
- PENNILESS.
- GIVE ME SOMETHING BETTER THAN THAT.

03:33.561 --> 03:35.519
OKAY, UH,

03:35.563 --> 03:38.130
MY PARENTS DON'T
EVEN TALK TO ME.

03:38.174 --> 03:40.872
YEAH? WELL, AT LEAST
YOUR MOM DIDN'T RUN OVER

03:40.916 --> 03:43.092
YOUR LEG IN HER VOLVO,
RIGHT? MINE DID.

03:43.135 --> 03:46.008
YEAH, BUT, SEE, MY MOM DOESN'T
GO INTO SPASTICATED SEIZURES

03:46.051 --> 03:48.619
- EVERY ONCE AND AGAIN.
- THAT'S RUDE, MISTER.

03:53.755 --> 03:55.060
- A DOGFIGHT?
- YEAH.

03:55.104 --> 03:57.062
- YEAH? YEAH?
- YEAH. YEAH.

03:57.106 --> 03:59.239
- ALL RIGHT.
- [ both growling ]

04:08.291 --> 04:10.293
HEY, BOBBY, MAN, THANKS
FOR LETTING ME CRASH.

04:10.337 --> 04:11.599
NO PROBLEM.

04:11.642 --> 04:13.688
- GOOD NIGHT.
- GOOD NIGHT.

04:19.781 --> 04:22.610
[ "Dream a Little Dream of Me" playing ]

04:32.489 --> 04:35.971
♪ STARS ♪

04:36.014 --> 04:39.975
♪ SHINING BRIGHT ABOVE YOU ♪

04:40.018 --> 04:42.586
♪ NIGHT BREEZES ♪

04:42.630 --> 04:44.588
♪ SEEM TO WHISPER ♪

04:44.632 --> 04:46.938
♪ "I LOVE YOU" ♪

04:46.982 --> 04:49.114
♪ BIRDS SINGING ♪

04:49.158 --> 04:53.510
♪ IN THE SYCAMORE TREE ♪

04:53.554 --> 04:55.773
♪ DREAM A LITTLE DREAM ♪

04:55.817 --> 05:00.517
♪ OF ME ♪

05:00.561 --> 05:03.303
♪ SAY NIGHTY-NIGHT ♪

05:03.346 --> 05:07.045
♪ AND KISS ME ♪

05:07.089 --> 05:09.918
♪ JUST HOLD ME TIGHT ♪

05:09.961 --> 05:13.748
♪ TELL ME YOU'LL MISS ME ♪

05:13.791 --> 05:16.316
♪ WHILE I'M ALONE ♪

05:16.359 --> 05:20.972
♪ AND BLUE AS CAN BE ♪

05:21.016 --> 05:23.148
♪ DREAM A LITTLE DREAM ♪

05:23.192 --> 05:27.370
♪ OF ME ♪

05:27.414 --> 05:30.330
♪ STARS FADING ♪

05:30.373 --> 05:35.204
♪ BUT I LINGER ON, DEAR ♪

05:35.247 --> 05:38.642
♪ STILL CRAVING ♪

05:38.686 --> 05:42.342
♪ YOUR KISS ♪

05:42.385 --> 05:44.344
♪ I'M LONGING ♪

05:44.387 --> 05:48.739
♪ TO LINGER TILL DAWN, DEAR ♪

05:48.783 --> 05:54.919
♪ JUST SAYING THIS ♪

05:54.963 --> 05:58.053
♪ SWEET DREAMS ♪

05:58.096 --> 06:02.144
♪ TILL SUNBEAMS FIND YOU ♪

06:02.187 --> 06:04.146
♪ SWEET DREAMS ♪

06:04.189 --> 06:06.409
♪ THAT LEAVE ALL WORRIES ♪

06:06.453 --> 06:08.977
♪ BEHIND YOU ♪

06:09.020 --> 06:11.936
♪ BUT IN YOUR DREAMS ♪

06:11.980 --> 06:15.113
♪ WHATEVER THEY BE ♪

06:15.157 --> 06:18.160
♪ DREAM A LITTLE DREAM ♪

06:18.203 --> 06:22.425
♪ OF ME ♪

06:22.469 --> 06:25.385
♪ DREAM A DREAM ♪

06:25.428 --> 06:28.126
♪ OF ME ♪

06:33.088 --> 06:35.830
♪ DREAM A LITTLE DREAM ♪

06:35.873 --> 06:39.311
♪ OF ME ♪

06:39.355 --> 06:41.357
[ cheering ]

06:43.446 --> 06:45.579
[ birds chirping ]

06:47.145 --> 06:48.408
GOOD MORNING.

06:48.451 --> 06:51.411
GENA,

06:51.454 --> 06:53.413
I HAD THIS FANTASTIC...

06:53.456 --> 06:55.502
DREAM. YOU ALWAYS
HAVE A DREAM.

06:55.545 --> 06:58.069
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR ABOUT YOUR
CRAZY DREAM RIGHT NOW, OKAY?

06:58.113 --> 07:00.681
IT WAS ABOUT THE OLD GUY THAT...
YOU KNOW, FROM THE SHORTCUT...

07:00.724 --> 07:03.031
THE SHORTCUT WE TAKE
EVERY DAY TO SCHOOL.

07:03.074 --> 07:05.425
WELL, HE WAS IN IT.

07:05.468 --> 07:09.254
BOBBY, THAT'S JUST STUPID.

07:09.298 --> 07:11.474
Man:
GENA, IT WAS IMPORTANT.

07:11.518 --> 07:13.476
[ horns honking ]

07:13.520 --> 07:16.958
"THERE ARE NONE SO BLIND
AS THOSE WHO WILL NOT SEE"...

07:17.001 --> 07:18.960
JEREMIAH 20.

07:19.003 --> 07:21.266
Gena:
HURRY UP, OR YOU'LL BE
WORKING ON A DREAM THEORY

07:21.310 --> 07:23.268
OF AN OLD MAN SURVIVING
A PUNCH IN THE NOSE.

07:23.312 --> 07:25.270
WE HAVE A GUEST COMING
THIS MORNING.

07:25.314 --> 07:27.751
Man:
IKE IS NOT A GUEST.
HE'S A DEPENDENT.

07:27.795 --> 07:30.711
I'M NOT SEEING ANYBODY TILL
I'VE DONE MY MEDITATION.

07:30.754 --> 07:32.495
YOU CAN GO DOWNSTAIRS
AND TELL HIM THAT.

07:32.539 --> 07:34.715
- HEY.
- CHILL OUT, MAN.

07:36.238 --> 07:38.849
WHY DID YOU MARRY ME?

07:38.893 --> 07:41.591
BECAUSE I SAW
THE OTHER HALF OF ME.

07:43.550 --> 07:44.768
I LOVE YOU.

07:44.812 --> 07:47.771
I LOVE YOU TOO.

07:47.815 --> 07:49.773
[ school bell ringing ]

07:49.817 --> 07:51.819
Gena:
I'LL SEE YOU DOWNSTAIRS.

08:05.397 --> 08:07.356
♪ I STUDY NUCLEAR SCIENCE ♪

08:07.399 --> 08:08.923
♪ I LOVE MY CLASSES ♪

08:08.966 --> 08:11.839
♪ I GOT A CRAZY TEACHER,
HE WEARS DARK GLASSES ♪

08:11.882 --> 08:13.841
♪ THINGS ARE GOING GREAT ♪

08:13.884 --> 08:16.800
♪ AND THEY'RE ONLY
GETTING BETTER ♪

08:16.844 --> 08:19.063
♪ I'M DOING ALL RIGHT ♪

08:19.107 --> 08:21.022
♪ GETTING GOOD GRADES ♪

08:21.065 --> 08:22.937
♪ THE FUTURE'S SO BRIGHT ♪

08:22.980 --> 08:25.722
♪ I'VE GOT TO WEAR SHADES ♪

08:25.766 --> 08:28.638
♪ I'VE GOT TO WEAR SHADES ♪

